    Add Spend Profile selector and custom per-phase monthly editor (#2)
    
    - Add spendProfile field to defaultInv: { type:'default', customPct:null }
    - Add buildSpendWeights() pure helper before generateCopperleafXLSX, resolving
      per-month weights from preset curves (S-curve/front/balanced/back-loaded)
      or custom per-phase percentage arrays
    - Replace all four flat perMonth = total/phMonths.length divisions in
      generateCopperleafXLSX with profile-weighted distributions:
      labour/contractor rows, non-LLT materials, LLT materials, commissioning rows
    - Add Spend Profile Card to InvestmentSetup between Timeline and Invoicing
      Milestones: five radio options (Default/WBS1/WBS2/WBS3/Custom), info note
      for preset profiles, and a five-tab custom editor with month-by-month % inputs,
      live bar visualisation, Even split/S-curve/Clear helpers, and sum validation
    
    Base estimate totals are unchanged — spend profile only redistributes monthly
    timing in the Copperleaf export, not the underlying cost calculations.

